{"type":"message","id":"ab1d1dbf","parentId":"beb25338","timestamp":"2026-03-24T17:16:44.662Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture. The pulse completed successfully. Let me summarize:\n\n1. The pulse ran and completed\n2. A mutation was proposed but got moved to the `rejected/` folder (previously it was a new file)\n3. The commit shows the new pulse log and a rejected mutation from the previous cycle\n4. The previous mutation (131516) was about the hybrid CFI×Freq scoring experiment design, but it was rejected (the new cycle moved it to rejected)\n\nLet me check the latest pulse log to see the most recent observation.","thinkingSignature":"0875d88295d474cdd9825d00b05672b1574080b8ec50d4be388e7c6bdb0fc94f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_psckmb4942bv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\memory\\session\\ | Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending | Select-Object -First 1 | ForEach-Object { $_.FullName }"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2048,"output":184,"cacheRead":12137,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14369,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774372600066}}
